Grove Extensions

The following features are original work by Cardene and contributors:
- Background parallel execution for Self Review
- Autonomous verification agent with 8-point quality checklist
- Auto-Fix functionality with TDD approach
- Cross Review support for multi-AI verification
- t-wada style TDD workflow integration
- Multi-language support (Japanese/English)
- Frontend design specifications workflow

For the complete list of Grove-specific features, see CHANGELOG.md.
